        "type": "rule",
        "text": "Once per turn, in your opponent\u2019s Shooting phase , when an enemy unit makes a ranged attack that targets a friendly REGIMENT unit within 3\" of this model, after that enemy unit has shot, this model can shoot as if it were your Shooting phase, but it must target only that enemy unit when doing so, and can only do so if that enemy unit is an eligible target.",
